image_analysis.description: A color photograph of a small bathroom. The image shows a white pedestal sink in the foreground with a small potted orchid sitting on its edge. To the right of the sink is a brown trash bin. Behind the sink is a bathtub with a sliding glass shower door. Two white towels are hanging over the towel bar on the shower door. The shower walls are lined with grey marble tiles. A wall-mounted light fixture is visible above the sink next to a black-framed mirror. Various toiletries, including soap and mouthwash, are on a shelf below the mirror.
image_analysis.layout: Vertical portrait orientation showing a bathroom interior.
